name: Trails
description: Trails was taken with many trial and errors. Had to fight against the surrounding islands, making their appearance with their harbor lights from far away. I stayed overexposed on the windy beach at night, on one of the only area of the island where I could catch some darkness. It's not easy to find in the very mountainous Sifnos. You can see the lights of Serifos appearing far away and exposing the horizon.
